class_summary <- ppbforce_clean_q321 %>% 
#  filter(!is.na(ht_in)) %>% 
  group_by(ppbforce_clean_q321$civil_mental) %>% 
  summarise(
    n                    = n(),
    mean                 = mean(force_officer_sum),
    `standard deviation` = sd(force_officer_sum),
    min                  = min(force_officer_sum),
    max                  = max(force_officer_sum)
  ) %>% 
  print()
